Blocking animation preload before playback
==========================================

Date: 2026-07-02

Purpose
-------
Avoid the first few seconds of dropped frames after the scaling-quality changes.

The scaling options caused the active displayed animation to often be a scaled
AnimatedImage wrapper. Those transformed frames were being preloaded in a
background thread while the playback timer started immediately, so the first
playback pass could compete with frame scaling/conversion.

This change keeps the existing playback structure but waits for the active
display image's animation frames to preload before starting the animation timer.

